room_title: Escape room "Lair of Lunacy" by The Escape Key in Salt Lake City
room_address: 250 E 300 S #380 Salt Lake City, UT 84111
room_description:
Are your wits about you? Prepare yourself for an adventure unlike any other! You will find yourself in dark and mysterious laboratory where something diabolical is taking place... Up to eight scientists must not only work together but use their skills of deduction and discovery in order to “survive” their time inside!

Plastic bones and fake blood. Recommended for 8 and up.
There is also the Lair of Lunacy room at the Provo location. Address: 443 N University Ave Provo, UT 84601. Phone number: 385-236-3409.
